{"title":"山之歌——吴旗红军胜利会师山感赋","authors":["孙晓杰"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":7,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山之歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——吴旗红军胜利会师山感赋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙晓杰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两双粗大的手紧握的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两颗强劲的心碰撞的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两块精神的高原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连接成，一片新大陆的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"选择一架山吧——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用山做背景，背景是厚重的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用山做碑石，碑石是巍峨的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用山做见证，见证是永恒的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山的逶迤的走势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在１９３５年１０月，吴旗的天空下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛是深情的怀抱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些褴褛的灰色军衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呈现出灰烬的颜色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但灰烬里面，历史的手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"触摸到铁骨铮铮的火啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正像热血燃烧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用弹洞和穿流在弹洞里的硝烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装饰的旗帜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在陕北的激情中，鼓荡，飘飞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像鹰的翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以大河的涛声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擦响宽阔的山壁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲般的山啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾经以冰雪，这冷酷的方式"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝视着稀薄的氧气里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰难喘息的红星。直到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她看见血迹斑斑的意志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咬碎了最后的草根"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便像埋下火种"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起了，胜利的朝日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山啊！永远是勇士的圣足"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前行的阶石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远是英雄的雕像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"完美的基座"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……是的，我们还热爱山吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些伟岸的灵魂里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岩石的坚毅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥土的质朴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树木的蓬勃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花朵的芬芳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溪水的果敢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们还能像，这一支"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长征在史诗里的灰色军旅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在山的面前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洒落，至纯至诚的热泪吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与山相望而行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不会是永久的孤旅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山的崇高和不朽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"必将与你会师"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的艰苦将是你的光荣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的尘污将是你的纯净"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的伤痛将是你的幸福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你呼啸的欢声啊——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿行在山的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绵延不绝的苍茫里"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}